column12: Plastics beaker, for liquid or paste or solid foodstuffs or detergents, has a lid welded to the beaker edge to seal the contents and ensure tamper-proof protection
column13: A plastics beaker, with a lid (20), is of a deep drawn or injection molded plastics or a compound material of plastics (5) and paper (6). The lid has at least one carrier layer (31) either with a peel layer (32) of a plastics material at the inner side of the lid at least at the lid edge, or the carrier has peeling characteristics. The plastics beaker, with a lid (20), is of a deep drawn or injection molded plastics or a compound material of plastics (5) and paper (6). The lid has at least one carrier layer (31) either with a peel layer (32) of a plastics material at the inner side of the lid at least at the lid edge, or the carrier has peeling characteristics. The lid with the carrier and peel layers is welded to the edge (4) of the container. The lid has a cut line (30a) where an opening can be torn out, at a gap from the outer circumference and along at least along an edge zone.

Die Erfindung betrifft ein Toleranzausgleichselement (13), das zwischen einer zumindest im Wesentlichen axialen Bodenfläche (5) einer Ventilaufnahme (4) eines Gehäuses (3) und eines axial in die Ventilaufnahme (4) einsetzbaren Ventilmoduls (2) anordenbar ist, wobei das Toleranzausgleichselement (13) wenigstens einen axial vorstehenden Vorsprung (16, 17, 18) mit einer axialen Aufstandsfläche (19) aufweist und Kegelstumpf-förmig ausgebildet ist. Dabei ist vorgesehen, dass der Vorsprung (16–18) als schiefer Kegelstumpf (20) ausgebildet ist. Ferner betrifft die Erfindung eine Ventileinheit (1).

column12: TOLERANCE EQUALIZATION ELEMENT AND VALVE UNIT HAVING SUCH A TOLERANCE EQUALIZATION ELEMENT
column13: The invention relates to a tolerance equalization element (13) which can be arranged between an at least substantially axial floor surface (5) of a valve receptacle (4) of a housing (3) and a valve module (2) which can be axially inserted into the valve receptacle (4), wherein the tolerance equalization element (13) has at least one axially protruding projection (16, 17, 18) having an axial contact area (19) and is designed having a truncated cone shape. According to the invention, the projection (16-18) is designed as an oblique truncated cone (20), wherein the point of the imaginary cone is arranged not vertically over the center point of the base surface of the truncated cone but shifted laterally perpendicular or radially thereto. The invention furthermore relates to a valve unit (1) having such a tolerance equalization element (13).
